{"tid":972770,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人反而想去翻科技冇咁發達嘅年代","createTime":"2019-01-07T15:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T03:44:09.000Z","uid":151745,"like":59,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4f01a557c25cfc106e3cbce7d50e02d668d9c4","tid":972770,"uid":151745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人反而想去翻科技冇咁發達嘅年代<br />\n<br />\n無可否認電子產品真係改變左人類嘅人明<br />\n<br />\n但係你地仲記唔記得以前細個冇電話用<br />\n<br />\n未有電腦煲劇未有youtube睇片嘅開心時光<br />\n<br />\n以前細細個真係幾個細路圍住個波已經好開心<br />\n<br />\n宜家大左個個出黎都係對住部電話係到禁禁禁<br />\n<br />\n連人與人最基本嘅溝通都愈黎愈少啦<br />\n<br />\n拍拖嘅出黎又係到咁 朋友出黎都係到咁 連屋企人食飯都係係到咁<br />\n<br />\n大家既然都係出黎禁電話咁仲出黎做乜？點解唔可以面對面講下野？真係有咩咁重要要對住部電話咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解無論親情愛情友情都去唔翻以前一樣？<br />\n<br />\n究竟係人大左心態唔一樣定係因為有左科技？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105ba9285c51ab9c00d6831dfe4f23d0ba92217f","tid":972770,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OINa46HeWg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOINa46HeWg8&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqMACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=42f0e985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OINa46HeWg8</a>"},{"pid":"6e8d954d0f615fe61e336ad75f9124d1f6ef1e93","tid":972770,"uid":151745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105ba9285c51ab9c00d6831dfe4f23d0ba92217f","tid":972770,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OINa46HeWg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOINa46HeWg8&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqMACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=42f0e985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OINa46HeWg8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"真係好心酸 唔知10年後仲有冇人識傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8db2a912bd6246f204a0dd17c2869f335fb733","tid":9